Miller Family 
Jill is the primary budget manager for a busy household of six, balancing a full-time career with the complex logistics of raising four children. 
She is married to Jack who is a mechanic that works long hours. She views her family’s finances as an important detail to keeping the family 
running smoothly. With children ranging from preschool to high school—all of which are heavily involved in competitive sports her daily 
focus is on tracking high-volume expenses like groceries, school fees, and utility costs that can quickly scale up in a large home.
